Package com.example.superqr

Class QRCode

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.superqr.QRCode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable
    public class QRCode
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    The QRCode class keeps track of the code, score, and geolocation of a QR code. This class handles handles hashing of the QRCode object into a score for the player.
